reviewText: Not a good movie Son stop watching:-(

The cover and the title itself is misleading. The pink rabbit plays a very small role. The movie was fine but I didn't get what I thought I was getting. I think my s7 y.o. would have been more interested if the pink rabbit played a larger role.
My 3yr and 7yr old nieces love it. I've lost count of how many times they've watched it.
